{"tid":1469322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要！請反思！年輕人的抗爭其實係幫左中共","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:17:02.000Z","uid":269617,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a606fba09347bf51f82522bd7c98d79168a3d964","tid":1469322,"uid":269617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:23:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家留意新聞，昨晚美國再一次向中國的關稅退讓，年青人的抗爭間接幫了中共。<br />\n<br />\n香港特別行政區首長昨天已默認，不能「撤」回條例是中央的意思。<br />\n<br />\n讀過法律和經濟，平常心分析，香港特殊經濟地位仍有利用價值。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">103萬人遊行當晚，美國宣佈對中國的貿易制裁限期延遲，之前雙方一直企硬。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n之後談判又没有進展。<br />\n<br />\n元朗一役，黑社會無差別打人，警察唔知死曬去邊，衝擊香港法治，沉默的商會出聲，<span style=\"color: red;\">沉默的中美談判再解凍，關於大豆等關稅問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n前兩天，香港的經濟命脈機場成為抗爭據點，<span style=\"color: red;\">昨晚美國又宣布對中國的關稅退讓。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每次香港亂，美國會退讓，中方用這條例作為中美貿易談判籌碼，把香港擺上枱，因為美國在香港的利益也不少。</span><br />\n<br />\n抗爭者請認清楚，如果你們繼續讓香港亂下去，只是幫中共，得益嘅係亞爺。<br />\n<br />\n為公義「發聲」 而不是「審判」者，請你們懂得政治經濟，世界局勢。<br />\n<br />\n轉載自Carol Chan<br />\n不一樣的生命作者</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"e46676e779d1f092984c8a7d66caed842df3de01","tid":1469322,"uid":181283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:25:53.000Z","msg":"少咁D野"},{"pid":"20b0a72c0746ccd39fd2fcc0bcb799138446187b","tid":1469322,"uid":269617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:26:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國其實只睇利益<br />\n<br />\n任何國家都係<br />\n<br />\n依個世界冇國家會為正義而放棄利益</span>"},{"pid":"398bd59f9c07ebee471ab35c8eebc80764849a88","tid":1469322,"uid":34154,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:28:52.000Z","msg":"呀侵有邊次唔係對支那讓少少步然後反口過佢一棟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4321d86d1a13f646e85e384141a8cbb3ea0465","tid":1469322,"uid":269617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:30:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以冷靜想一想嗎？<br />\n<br />\n大家流血被捕<br />\n<br />\n卻反而益了老共<br />\n<br />\n扺咩？<br />\n<br />\n但現實就係咁冇天理！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"627350b699ae18f281ed9a50194a665fb36080fa","tid":1469322,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ab2e90ca0f042ebd3725141e122d166932f9055","tid":1469322,"uid":22360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:28.000Z","msg":"如果美國希望保留佢哋喺香港嘅利益，佢哋應該要做返啲實事<br />\n<br />\n我亦都唔係好相信有人會用自己個春袋去威脅其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3f8b217a08886806f6c3629844a2904b993282","tid":1469322,"uid":269617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"627350b699ae18f281ed9a50194a665fb36080fa","tid":1469322,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[black]你甘心入集中營？[/black]</span></span>"},{"pid":"67d7ee7cea168d8a29b2423db15c64e072677eb6","tid":1469322,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"佢而家製造新疆模式，就係要後生仔幫手去形成個環境"},{"pid":"cb49eb705be9684e44713c857a232a8938ba4cb4","tid":1469322,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:38:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"963adc4ef65602668ac45d108d7effc8248273f4","tid":1469322,"uid":269617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:50:15.000Z","msg":"我心痛至極<br />\n<br />\n但冇人聽也唔知可以點<br />\n<br />\n你們是白白犧牲了"},{"pid":"f608c68fcbb856db06ded3f5e1217b2f2a0d6364","tid":1469322,"uid":269617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">